@section System hierarchy and groups

Goptical allows arranging components of the optical system in a hierarchical manner. Optical component classes all inherit from the Sys::Element (@pxref{Sys_Element_class_reference}) class. Elements which inherit from the Sys::Group (@pxref{Sys_Group_class_reference}) class can contain nested elements.

Each element has a local coordinate system and stores a Math::Transform (@pxref{Math_Transform_3_class_reference})<3> object which describes its translation and rotation relative to the parent coordinate system.

